title.rendered: Natan. Couture Presentation SS 2023 during Haute Couture Week.

content.rendered:
Natan. Couture Presentation Spring Summer 2023 during Haute Couture Week.

NATAN women are metamorphosed for this years Jubilee. And theyve landed serving a whole new spectrum of modern chic, glamour, color and light, left and right. Can you feel it?

Like a full breath of fresh air, their brisk walk throbbing at the beat of a new breezy day, strutting down all platforms and standing high and tall on rotating pedestals, elevated and sculptural. Spinning round and round, to be admired from every angle by the hordes at the other side of the screen in this Instagram-obsessed era. They demonstrate exuberance and elegance, energy-enhancing luminous looks, and dazzling come-hither moves engineered to last a never-ending festive summer day.

From blinding daytime to fiery sunsets and sumptuous nighttime. Its the dream party that keeps on giving, only to be matched with a full palette of richly detailed statement silhouettes, playful and eye-popping vibrant gowns, effervescent, light-reflecting and snazzy Couture. From one twilight to the next, from fun and joyful to sophisticated and lavishly cool. Give in to the enchanting NATAN spell and dance the summer day and night away


Text and Photo: Press Natan

More on: www.natan.be @natancouture

Thanks: Caroline Charles Communication @carolinecharlescommunication


By Senior Fashion Editor 24FashionTV: Christina V Henningstad @christina_henningstad
